[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2020.07.21"]
[UTCTime "03:10:33"]

18... exd4? { Incorrectly exchanging pawns. This only helps White's piece breathe more easily and allow more exchanges. } (18... e4! 19. Nd2 f5 { White's pieces are now even more trapped, while Black aims to breka open the f-file to double the rooks. }) 19. Nxd4 { White now has the semi-open d-file and a free bishop next after Bb1. } *


