21... Rfb8 22. Bc1?! { Not necessarily game-changing, but it is still a bit passive, giving the initiative to Black. } (22. Rxc6! { Allowing Black to take on b2, but White gets two pawns in the process and active pieces! } 22... Rxb2 23. Rxd6) *


