1... a5 { Great move! White's knight is not on an outpost, so freely kick it backwards to a future of inactivity } (1... Bxb4? { You've just traded your strong bishop for White's knight, which is not even on an outpost. White will recapture with the a-pawn and free up the Ra1 as well. No good! } 2. axb4) *


