1. c4 Nf6 2. Nc3 g6 3. g3 Bg7 4. Bg2 O-O 5. e4 d6 6. Nge2 Nbd7 7. O-O e5 8. d3 a5 { [%cal Gd7c5] } 9. h3 Nc5 10. f4 { f5 is a big cramp for Black. } { [%csl Gf4][%cal Gf4f5] } 10... exf4 { [%cal Gf6h5,Gc5e6] } 11. Nxf4 c6 12. Be3 Qe7 13. Qd2 Nfd7 14. d4 { Full control over the center. } 14... Ne6 15. Rae1 Nf6 { [%cal Gd4d5,Ge4e5] } 16. Nxe6 fxe6 17. d5 Qc7 { [%cal Ge4e5] } 18. e5 { [%csl Gd6,Gf6] } 18... Ne8 (18... dxe5 19. d6 Qd8 20. Na4 { The protected passed pawn on d6 is a big thorn in Black's position. }) 19. Rxf8+ Bxf8 20. c5!! { This gets a white pawn on d6 by force } 20... exd5 21. exd6 { [%csl Gd6] } 21... Nxd6 22. cxd6 Qxd6 23. Bf4 Qc5+ 24. Kh1 Bf5 25. g4 Bd7 26. Ne4 Qe7 27. Bg5 Qg7 28. Nf6+ Kh8 29. Rf1 Bb4 30. Qf4 Rf8 31. Bh6 { Black resigned 1-0 } *


