1. c4 Nf6 2. Nc3 g6 3. g3 Bg7 4. Bg2 O-O 5. e4 e5 6. Nge2 d6 7. O-O Nc6 8. d3 Nd7 9. f4 exf4 10. Bxf4 { [%cal Gd3d4,Gf6h5] } 10... Nd4 11. Qd2 Nc5 { [%csl Gh1][%cal Gf4g5,Gf7f6] } 12. Nxd4 Bxd4+ 13. Kh1 c6 14. Bh6 Bg7 (14... Re8 15. Ne2 { Either way, Black's bishop has to move or get exchanged. Then White plays d4 with the full center. }) 15. Bxg7 Kxg7 16. d4 Nd7 { [%cal Gf1f2,Gf1f4] } 17. Rf4 { [%cal Ga1f1,Gh7h6,Gf4h4] } 17... h6 18. Raf1 Qe7 19. b4 a5 { [%csl Gc3][%cal Gc4c5,Ge4e5] } 20. a3 axb4 21. axb4 { [%cal Gc4c5] } 21... Ra3 22. Qb2 Ra8 23. c5 Ra7 24. cxd6 Qxd6 25. e5 Qe7 26. Ne4 Nb6 { [%cal Gc8e6,Gb6d5] } 27. e6! { Opening up the long a1-h8 diagonal. Discovered checks everywhere } 27... f5 28. d5+ Kh7 29. d6 Qxe6 { [%cal Gf4h4] } 30. Qd4 { [%csl Gb6,Ga7] } 30... Nd5 31. Rh4 Kg8 32. Rxh6 Nf6 33. Rxg6+ { 1-0 } *


