[UTCTime "02:16:38"]

13... Rxc3!? { An exchange sacrifice in the Sicilian Najdorf to permanently destroy White's pawn structure. Black gets a lot of compensation for the exchange as a result. } 14. bxc3 Na4 { The c3 pawn is a goner, and Black can finish development pretty quickly thereafter } *


